Data Visualization with ggplot2 (W7)

2019-10-24

ggplot: layers of graphics

  1. ggplot(data = mpg)
  2. ggplot(data = mpg) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy))
  3. ggplot(data = mpg) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy)) +
  geom_smooth(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy))

  4. ggplot(data = mpg) +
  geom_smooth(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy)) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy))
